# Rails 8 Personal Brand Agent Rule

## Read context first
- Truoc khi code, doc cac tai lieu trong `docs/` co lien quan den task.
- Uu tien theo thu tu: `PROJECT_SCOPE` -> `FEATURE_ROADMAP` -> tai lieu ky thuat.

## Scope and phase discipline
- Chi implement tinh nang thuoc phase dang duoc yeu cau.
- Khong mo rong scope ngoai roadmap neu chua co chi dao ro.

## Rails-first implementation
- Uu tien Rails conventions, service object chi tao khi can thiet.
- Uu tien SSR + Hotwire, tranh tang JS complexity som.

## Quality gates
- Moi thay doi phai co test phu hop (model/request/system/job).
- Dam bao pass lint va security checks:
  - `bin/rubocop`
  - `bin/brakeman --no-pager`
  - `bin/bundler-audit`
  - `bin/importmap audit`

## Public page SEO baseline
- Route public moi phai co title, meta description, canonical.
- Noi dung chia se can co Open Graph/Twitter metadata.

## Documentation updates are required
- Thay doi model/flow/SEO phai cap nhat file `docs/` lien quan.
- Quyet dinh ky thuat quan trong phai ghi vao `docs/DECISIONS.md`.

## Security baseline
- Khong commit secrets hoac key files.
- Sanitize markdown/rich-text output truoc khi render.
